Package: hmsidwR
Title: Collection of data and function used in the Health Metrics and the Spread of Infectious Diseases with R
    book
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Federica", "Gazzelloni", , "fede.gazzelloni@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4285-611"))
Description: This package provides data sets and author's functions used
    in the Health Metrics and the Spread of Infectious Diseases with R
    book from CRC Press. The book provides the tools for calculating the DALYs (YLLs+YLDs), and other important health metrics.
    It also shows the R code for modeling infectious diseases with machine learning. Finally,
    allows the user to understand how to visualize the results and making maps.
